rComments: Lab talks were helpful and clarified some of the material covered in class. Made the lab sessions a lot more fun and was really approachable both during lab sessions and outside of class. A great lab instructor!

Great lab instructor, super helpful, nice and approachable. He will consider giving you an extension if you are having a really tough week (if you have many assignments, tests, etc). Labs are fun, reports are pretty extensive, but John explains concepts really well and you learn a ton from the labs and the reports. Overall a wonderful instructor.

DeBackere was the lab coordinator for CHM338 and he made the lab a lot more fun; his in-lab talks were really helpful and relevant for the reports and the lecture section, and he was really approchable and provided good feedback on the reports. If you get him for the lab section youre in luck because he's great.
